title: MPT Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in interview for 04 Medical Officer Posts
description: The Mumbai Port Trust has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 04 Medical Officer Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their MBBS, DNB, and MS/MD can apply for the MPT Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can attend the interview.
